    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle is a practical opportunity for anyone seeking reliable basic transportation or a solid project at an accessible price point. It shows its age and is best suited for a buyer who values straightforward value, but it still offers plenty of potential for the right owner. An honest, affordable option that makes sense for commuters, first-time buyers, or anyone looking to keep costs down.",
