    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly car with plenty of life and potential left in it? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, runs, and can be a great fit for someone who needs simple, affordable wheels or enjoys a little tinkering on the side. It\u2019s priced with its condition in mind and offers a lot of value for the money. If you want an honest car at a fair price, come take a look.",
