      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-minded driver/project with good bones and plenty of usable life left. Starts, runs, and drives, with a dependable powertrain and straightforward mechanical layout that makes it a great candidate for a daily beater, first car, or weekend fixer-upper. Cosmetic wear and age-related blemishes are present, but the car still offers practical transportation and strong value for someone who appreciates a no-nonsense setup. If you want an affordable car with real potential and low barrier to entry, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
