    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of scrappy charm that makes you look twice\u2014a well-traveled machine with plenty of stories already written and room for a few more. It\u2019s not pretending to be a showroom darling; instead, it offers character, presence, and a budget-friendly path into ownership for someone who appreciates potential. Perfect for a handy driver, a weekend tinkerer, or anyone wanting inexpensive wheels with personality, this is the sort of car that could be a faithful sidekick, a practical backup, or your next satisfying project.",
      "price": 5900.0,
